headline: AbbVie Announces 20 Recipients of Migraine Career Catalyst Award™
summary: AbbVie (NYSE: ABBV) today announced the 20 recipients of its second annual AbbVie Migraine Career Catalyst Award™ contest, an initiative that helps people living with migraine pursue their career and professional development goals. Each winner received $2,500 in financial support to invest in opportunities that advance their aspirations, from continued education and training to creating healthier, more supportive work environments.
